Devgree - Frequently Asked Questions

Discover what makes Devgree the preferred choice for tech professionals.

Personalized Portfolio

Showcase your skills, projects, and accomplishments in a customizable and professional layout.

FAQ: How can I customize my portfolio layout?

Skills Assessments

Engage in quizzes and assessments to measure your technical proficiency.

FAQ: Where can I share my assessment results?

Privacy Controls

Decide which parts of your portfolio are public or private.

FAQ: How do I set privacy controls for my portfolio?

Video Integration

Embed videos from platforms like YouTube, Vimeo, or TikTok.

FAQ: How do I add videos to my portfolio?

Portfolio Analytics

Get a view of your portfolio's performance, including visitor metrics.

FAQ: What analytics can I view for my portfolio?

Testimonials & References

Add testimonials from mentors, colleagues, or clients.

FAQ: How do I add testimonials to my portfolio?

Achievement Badges

Display badges from courses, certifications, or other platforms.

FAQ: How can I showcase my achievement badges?

Skill Endorsements

Allow peers and mentors to endorse your skills.

FAQ: How do skill endorsements work?

Unified Code Display

Aggregate your repositories from multiple platforms.

FAQ: How do I integrate my code repositories?

ATS-Compatible Resume Generation

Generate a professional ATS-compatible resume from your portfolio data.

FAQ: How do I generate a resume from my portfolio?

Direct Contact

Enable potential employers to contact you directly via your portfolio.

FAQ: How does the direct contact feature work?

Intelligent Resume Import

Import your resume and let our AI system populate your profile.

FAQ: How do I import my resume?

); }; export default FAQs;
